Silence.

"So we can talk about the Goddess." Konvexen finished.

Z0ya, trying not to 
#- show flattery, said, "Um, sure. 7 o'clock?"

Konvexen was astounded. A date? With a person! Not just a person, someone who identifies as a girl! Would he finally get to pop his cyber cherry? 
"YES! 7 is fine with me! More than fine! See 
